snippet.title: Seeds of Calamity Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
First came the Calamity, then came the healing. Live your farming fantasy life. Study battle magic, explore ancient dungeons. Help your neighbors, grow with your Spellbook Companion. Become part of the great recovery.

Wishlist Seeds of Calamity on Steam Now!: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1780070/Seeds_of_Calamity/
